WEBVTT

00:00:00.901 --> 00:00:04.407
Your company launches
a search for an open position.

00:00:04.848 --> 00:00:07.214
The applications start rolling in,

00:00:07.238 --> 00:00:10.226
and the qualified candidates
are identified.

00:00:10.613 --> 00:00:12.986
Now the choosing begins.

00:00:13.780 --> 00:00:19.458
Person A: Ivy League,
4.0, flawless resume,

00:00:19.482 --> 00:00:21.366
great recommendations.

00:00:21.390 --> 00:00:23.133
All the right stuff.

00:00:23.784 --> 00:00:28.785
Person B: state school,
fair amount of job hopping,

00:00:28.809 --> 00:00:33.039
and odd jobs like cashier
and singing waitress.